Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:10.99,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:19.20,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:31.51,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.84,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The party headed to the Witches' Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:42.31,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,to break the curse that Vetto \Nhad placed on Asta's arms,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:44.89,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and they found Vanessa in a wretched state.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:46.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Miz Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.34,0:00:47.40,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:53.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you think you are,\N but get your foot off of her right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:56.61,main,Witch queen,0000,0000,0000,,You must be the brat \NVanessa was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:59.72,main,Witch queen,0000,0000,0000,,This foolish little thing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:04.44,main,Witch queen,0000,0000,0000,,told me she'd become my slave and \Nlive out the rest of her days here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:07.67,main,Witch queen,0000,0000,0000,,in exchange for healing your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:09.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Miz Vanessa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:12.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save Vanessa,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:15.67,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the party began their battle with \Nthe Queen of Witches, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:20.92,main,Witch queen,0000,0000,0000,,They were much faster than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.40,0:01:25.25,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,New enemies arrived at the Witches' Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:26.94,main,Witch queen,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:33.44,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Spirit Magic: Salamander's Breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:38.15,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Witnessing how powerful the enemy was,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.15,0:01:40.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the Queen of Witches healed Asta's arms
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:42.74,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and let him protect the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:50.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is great! They're completely better!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:53.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.95,0:01:55.21,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:02:01.97,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the Queen of Witches's healing \Nmagic, Asta's arms were better than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:05.89,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His battle with Fana, who was\N filled with hatred, began.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:10.15,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:14.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on! I'll just keep throwing \Nyour attacks right back at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:30.75,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1023,1)}Flames of Hatred
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:52.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just keep throwing your \Nattacks right back at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:56.37,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:59.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:04.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:09.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just keep throwing your attacks right \Nback at you over and over and over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:15.85,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.12,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he's built up a lot of stress
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:15.85,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,since he couldn't use his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:20.81,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:23.15,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,This time we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:24.53,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,destroy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.66,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:28.74,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Spirit Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:33.79,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Salamander's Talon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:51.71,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:53.80,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:55.48,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's so powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.61,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Salamander,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:02.97,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,said to have the highest attack \Npower of the Four Great Spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:07.91,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against a spirit that matches \Nthe military power of an entire nation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:20.67,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.17,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits are mana-based lifeforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:26.49,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's anti-magic sword can \Nslash apart mana itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:26.49,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hot, hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was scary! But it's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:34.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're so lucky! I want a Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:34.22,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:39.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But that old guy, Vetto, was much \Nfaster and had better senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:42.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:44.23,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,...has a chance of winning this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:50.74,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... Watching you makes \Nbeing scared seem silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:02.84,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... Why are these flames so powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.50,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's like throwing water on burning rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:12.35,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm basically just wasting mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:16.82,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Asta and the others are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:22.49,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you hurt us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:23.54,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.40,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time for our counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.66,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:34.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Let's sit down \Nand talk this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:35.87,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:38.17,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:40.29,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,She's not someone you can just talk to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's with all this hate business?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:44.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly do you hate so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:49.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind telling me why you \Nhate the Clover Kingdom so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:54.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to understand \Neach other when all we ever do is fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:02.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.94,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:09.90,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:11.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:12.66,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:24.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend also really hated us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:26.96,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The ones you broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:30.51,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Our golden dreams and our bonds of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.89,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:37.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And... he was full of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:40.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:44.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we just understand each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:03.69,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Licht, is that person human?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:13.63,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:20.64,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,There's something strange about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:23.45,flashback,Wizard King,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that this will become
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:26.65,flashback,Wizard King,0000,0000,0000,,a world where our peoples can \Nlive side by side as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:28.69,flashback,Wizard king,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:32.40,flashback,Wizard king,0000,0000,0000,,Elves' mana is truly amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:36.77,flashback,Wizard king,0000,0000,0000,,If we combine that with our techniques \Nin creating magical items,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:39.69,flashback,Wizard king,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to make this place \Neven more prosperous and safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:43.16,flashback,Wizard king,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best to live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:47.67,flashback,Elf,0000,0000,0000,,We wish you happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:59.83,flashback,Elf,0000,0000,0000,,The mana is giving us its blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:04.89,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy that our child will be welcomed \Ninto this world with your blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:08.31,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,This child is our future,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.64,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,the one who'll bring the \Nelves and humans together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.93,flashback,Elf,0000,0000,0000,,The humans are attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.67,flashback,Elf 2,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:31.49,flashback,Elf 3,0000,0000,0000,,My love...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:36.37,flashback,Elf 2,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:39.72,flashback,Elf 4,0000,0000,0000,,Only that human knows where we live!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:42.47,flashback,Elf 5,0000,0000,0000,,He... He must've betrayed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:53.00,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:58.42,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:01.73,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:06.75,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Who would believe you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.77,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:37.53,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Can you handle all of my hatred?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:40.28,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a third eye, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That thing just got bigger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:07.81,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:12.02,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:22.55,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did it get bigger, it's using \Nmagic with different attributes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:25.03,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, give us a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:29.79,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Let the flames of my \Nhatred burn you to ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:42.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to bring out my special move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.91,main,Akimo,0000,0000,0000,,She's no ordinary mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.42,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:25.30,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:38.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:41.07,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The wave of hot air was \Nenough to blow me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:44.15,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to get closer to her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:49.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Miz Vanessa, Finral, are you guys all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:52.82,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhat. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:56.66,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Her insane amount of magic is \Ncreating a mana force field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:59.46,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having a hard time manipulating space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:04.58,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The second I put my magic\Nthread out, it gets burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:06.26,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That magic power is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:09.21,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the power of spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:12.64,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a god incarnate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.56,italics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:26.76,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Cradle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:34.75,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.25,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:40.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I keep putting out the fires in \Nthe forest, but there's no end to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:41.75,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have to extinguish...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:48.19,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck is that thing? It's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:51.05,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,L-Looks like I'll have to \Nextinguish the source first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:53.01,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle uses water magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And water can beat fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:03.48,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's evaporating...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:10.99,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Spirit Magic: Salamander's Talon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:16.93,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:18.14,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:19.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.99,main,noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:25.61,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'm the one who uses water magic,\Nso I have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.97,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this... I know I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:38.57,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this, I can do this, I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:39.85,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:44.28,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You've been damaged goods \Never since you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:47.86,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.79,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,The only way you managed \Nto pull off the attack
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:54.24,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,at the Water Temple is because \Nyou let your rage take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.01,0:14:58.20,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,You're a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:06.14,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:10.72,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:25.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle! You're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:27.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:31.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything about that flame!\N I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:35.81,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on! \NYou can do anything if you have the guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.66,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:38.31,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,He's so loud. My ears are ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:38.62,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You hear me, Noelle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:42.66,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You can figure anything out with guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:41.41,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta?! You're a bit too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:46.02,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Finral! Why are you plugging your ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:49.68,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Feel this wonderful breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:49.68,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You got this, Noelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:50.76,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:57.61,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip, Noelle. \NJust as Asta gave me courage...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.68,top,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:02.23,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to tell me! \NI'll do it, Stupidsta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:06.02,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to give Asta courage, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:07.25,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:11.57,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:16.53,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'll probably only be \Nable to use Sea Dragon's Roar once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.04,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet everything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.87,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,on this one attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:29.88,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a failure anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:34.63,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:48.61,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,She dodged it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:50.12,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:55.95,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.30,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:17.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whoa! That's our Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:17.51,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:25.52,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:30.20,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that, Asta? That's my true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:32.23,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yay, I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:34.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:38.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's my comrade! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:41.24,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle's attack managed \Nto subdue the salamander.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.86,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our only chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:43.99,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Next...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.43,top,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:50.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Now it's finally time \Nfor my special move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:52.67,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:58.43,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Mineral Creation Magic: Harpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.24,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:02.97,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! How is she able to use \Nmagic besides flame magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:04.35,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's so not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:07.02,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:16.07,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Recovery Magic: Phoenix Robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:21.09,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,And she can use recovery magic, too! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:25.14,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And this spell, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:27.71,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:30.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:35.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't happen to have a brother
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:37.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,with a really pale face \Nand spiky hair, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's over on the other side \Nof the forest right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:55.07,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:59.32,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anyone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:05.70,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,If I have any siblings, they're Licht\N and the people of the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:09.23,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Know their grudge against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:12.08,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll massacre every last one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get through to her at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:19.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to stop her with my \Nspecial move before she recovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:24.05,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a sec, Asta! What's this \Nspecial move you keep talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:25.85,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:29.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Glad you asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:33.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I'm gonna hold out \Nboth swords in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:36.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and charge straight through \Nthe air at super speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:37.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I call it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:39.83,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,How could you possibly do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:41.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I can't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:45.53,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Not without us, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:48.79,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You always come up with the craziest ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:51.29,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Let us help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:56.79,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... Remember what I said earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:20:01.00,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends are there to help you win \Nagainst a fate you can't defeat on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:02.18,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That attack of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:06.14,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,will end up being incredibly powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:09.51,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.15,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:29.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you kill anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:37.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bull Thrust!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:48.89,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:53.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My special move was a complete success!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:01.59,italics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:11.86,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Licht...
