Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:50.34,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.93,0:22:54.93,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Over and Over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.65,0:22:53.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Over and Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:58.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:02.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just keep throwing your attacks right \Nback at you over and over and over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:15.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me with all the narutos you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:19.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just eat all the narutos you throw at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:28.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me with all the natto you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:31.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}natto{\i0} gonna let it get me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:35.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ew! It's all over my swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.32,0:23:37.41,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to be stabbed by those swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.32,0:23:38.89,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, you stupid natto!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:42.52,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Asta! We defeated Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.52,0:23:45.98,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 60: \N"Defectors' Atonement."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:54.00,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 60\N\N{\fs18} Defectors' Atonement
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:51.19,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,No, Charmy. "Atonement" isn't a kind of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.19,0:23:53.82,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's when you make up for \Nsomething bad you did.
